  <entry>
    <title>上层目录的git无法跟踪子目录中clone 下的项目</title>
    <url>/2024/02/21/%E4%B8%8A%E5%B1%82%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%E7%9A%84git%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E8%B7%9F%E8%B8%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%ADclone-%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>正式提交一次blog。内容呢？思来想去，不如就以搭建项目过程中遇到的git问题及解法为内容吧！</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<h1 id="1-问题描述："><a href="#1-问题描述：" class="headerlink" title="1.问题描述："></a>1.问题描述：</h1><p>上层目录的git无法跟踪子目录中clone 下的项目</p>
<h1 id="2-目录树形图："><a href="#2-目录树形图：" class="headerlink" title="2.目录树形图："></a>2.目录树形图：</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.</span><br><span class="line">└── A</span><br><span class="line">    ├── B</span><br><span class="line">    │   └── .git</span><br><span class="line">    │       ├── branches</span><br><span class="line">    │       ├── hooks</span><br><span class="line">    │       ├── info</span><br><span class="line">    │       ├── objects</span><br><span class="line">    │       │   ├── info</span><br><span class="line">    │       │   └── pack</span><br><span class="line">    │       └── refs</span><br><span class="line">    │           ├── heads</span><br><span class="line">    │           └── tags</span><br><span class="line">    └── .git</span><br><span class="line">        ├── branches</span><br><span class="line">        ├── hooks</span><br><span class="line">        ├── info</span><br><span class="line">        ├── objects</span><br><span class="line">        │   ├── info</span><br><span class="line">        │   └── pack</span><br><span class="line">        └── refs</span><br><span class="line">            ├── heads</span><br><span class="line">            └── tags</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1 id="3-解法"><a href="#3-解法" class="headerlink" title="3.解法"></a>3.解法</h1><ol>
<li>想办法删B文件夹下的.git文件夹<ul>
<li>git rm -r path</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>清空A文件夹git缓存中B文件夹，再手动添加B文件夹<ul>
<li>git rm -r –cached path</li>
<li>git add path</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<p>解法1，2均可</p>
]]></content>
